72
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,630
professional conversion,

73
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:33,720
and lost item conversion.

74
00:03:34,880 --> 00:03:35,930
In legal provisions, they correspond to

75
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:37,310
Article 252,

76
00:03:37,340 --> 00:03:40,880
Article 253 and Article 254 respectively.

