141
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:47,550
Lastly, reach out your hand to the other party.

142
00:06:47,550 --> 00:06:50,010
Next, we arranged some time for discussion.

143
00:06:50,210 --> 00:06:52,520
After 30 minutes of discussion,

144
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:54,790
