145
00:06:54,790 --> 00:06:55,320
Start.

146
00:06:55,430 --> 00:06:57,960
-Nice to work with you.
-Nice to work with you.

147
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:02,410
Excuse me, teacher.

148
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:03,160
Yes?

149
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:05,580
Are you talking to me?

150
00:07:05,580 --> 00:07:06,100
Yes.

151
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:07,800
So you think I'm a teacher.

152
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:11,530
