153
00:07:11,900 --> 00:07:12,700
Here?

154
00:07:13,070 --> 00:07:15,000
Have you asked your group members?

155
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:16,040
No.

156
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,770
Please solve the problem within your group first.

157
00:07:18,770 --> 00:07:20,830
There will be no teachers when you enter the workforce.

158
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,610
Yes.

159
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:28,410
Don't tell them so easily.

160
00:07:30,980 --> 00:07:34,000
If she can't communicate with the people around her actively,

161
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:36,130
