164
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:43,290
No, I don't understand it at all.

165
00:07:49,140 --> 00:07:50,460
I'm back.

166
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,520
-Good work.
-Good work.

167
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:56,170
Welcome back.

168
00:07:56,550 --> 00:08:00,490
Perfect timing. I've got a delicious pudding for you.

169
00:08:02,340 --> 00:08:02,920
Okay.

170
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:05,030
Um.

171
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:07,640
What, you don't like pudding?

172
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:11,660
No, I like it a lot.

173
00:08:12,440 --> 00:08:13,440
I wish I could dive

174
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,660
