175
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,210
Please. Please. Dive in it.

176
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,900
Did something happen?

177
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:31,980
No.

178
00:08:33,210 --> 00:08:34,240
How should I put it?

179
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,100
Well.

180
00:08:36,110 --> 00:08:38,350
I think Mr. Chiba is amazing.

181
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,270
Our ways of thinking

182
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:51,010
are completely different.

183
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:57,760
Sakawa.

184
00:09:00,130 --> 00:09:00,920
Yes?

185
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:04,410
You said before that

186
00:09:05,250 --> 00:09:06,450
those with hearing impairments

187
00:09:06,450 --> 00:09:08,270
