222
00:11:28,290 --> 00:11:28,880
Taichi.

223
00:11:32,850 --> 00:11:33,540
Taichi.

224
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:35,890
Oh.

225
00:11:38,010 --> 00:11:39,070
What are you doing?

226
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,940
Ah, look at you.

227
00:11:41,060 --> 00:11:42,920
