228
00:11:46,290 --> 00:11:46,690
Yes?

229
00:11:51,530 --> 00:11:52,640
Well, Kouhei.

230
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:54,770
What?

231
00:11:59,520 --> 00:12:02,050
