232
00:12:04,110 --> 00:12:04,550
What?

233
00:12:08,650 --> 00:12:09,140
Well.

234
00:12:10,360 --> 00:12:11,690
Just forget what I said.

235
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:15,450
