239
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:22,930
Did you get into a fight again?

240
00:12:22,930 --> 00:12:23,300
What?

241
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,380
-What did you do?
-It's not like that.

242
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:26,940
