251
00:12:57,830 --> 00:12:58,890
What you want to do?

252
00:13:00,220 --> 00:13:00,840
Yes.

253
00:13:02,330 --> 00:13:03,390
How should I put it?

254
00:13:04,090 --> 00:13:05,950
I just have some thought about it.

255
00:13:07,900 --> 00:13:09,760
